article.headline: Allen scores 19 to lead Utah Valley over Cal Baptist 69-46
article.description: — Drake Allen scored 19 points as Utah Valley beat Cal Baptist 69-46 on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Allen scores 19 to lead Utah Valley over Cal Baptist 69-46
article.story: RIVERSIDE, Calif. -- — Drake Allen scored 19 points as Utah Valley beat Cal Baptist 69-46 on Thursday night. Allen added five rebounds and three steals for the Wolverines (11-14, 6-8 Western Athletic Conference). Ethan Potter totaled 12 points and Caleb Stone-Carrawell scored 11. The Lancers (14-10, 7-6) were led by Kendal Coleman with 12 points and 10 rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
